# MPGS server URL for a packaged (non-proxied) build. Leave empty for browser/
# Tauri dev, which proxies through Vite. A packaged Tauri build defaults to
# http://127.0.0.1:8080 when this is unset. Packaged builds only accept that
# origin or http://localhost:8080 because the desktop CSP permits exactly these.
VITE_MPGS_API_BASE=
